data.description: L@@k at this one!!! $30,000 in seller concessions!!! Use the money to buy down the interest rate, buy out mortgage insurance, apply towards closing cost or use it for a shop! House sits on .80 acres in the heart of Piedmont and is loaded with amenities. This custom built home offers 4 oversized bed rooms, 3 full bath, 2 half bath large study, large mudroom, bonus room with theater equipment 103” viewing area, perfect for movie night or game day. Tankless water heater, soft close hinges, Bluetooth speakers on back patio. Neighborhood offers pavilion with playground and pond. Ready to move in before the holidays. Schedule your showing today
